dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents hydrography linework for Dane County, Wisconsin in April 2005. The dataset was originally published by the Dane County Land Information Office on March 4, 2008.[This is a comprehensive, county-wide dataset of 2,400-scale hydrography polygons in Dane County, Wisconsin.]
